        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Ant.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " iii. 7. 6) says that the high priest’s mitre was like that of all the other priests, but another word is used (see ",
        "children": []
